Training and support were provided as follows:\r1.Peer walkthroughs will be conducted on a monthly basis school-wide.\r2.Weekly Goal Setting and monitoring of data.\r3.Quarterly student monitoring meetings with the principal.\r4.Building Capacity through our TNT Team\r5.Building Leadership with PD provided by UCSD Results & Bonnie McGrath\r6.Cohort Collaboration\r7.Go Math Training provided by the district\r8.Achieve 3000 & SIPPS training provided by the district\r9.Wilda Storm PD and Coaching model\r\rFor the 2016-17 School year our focus is on Writing Across the Curriculum.
